## 9. 测试

### 使用 MCP Inspector

```bash
# 1. 启动 MCP 服务器
npx ts-node-dev --respawn apps/service-ai-platfrom/src/main.ts

# 2. 启动 Inspector（UI）
npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector@0.16.2

# 连接至 http://localhost:9001/mcp 进行交互测试
```

### CLI 手动测试

```bash
# 列出工具
curl -X POST http://localhost:9001/mcp \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"method":"tools/list","params":{}}'

# 调用工具
curl -X POST http://localhost:9001/mcp \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"search_low_price_flights","arguments":{"departure":"北京","arrival":"上海"}}}'

# 列出资源
curl -X POST http://localhost:9001/mcp \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"method":"resources/list","params":{}}'
```

